ontent/uploads/2021/06/31151144/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-outside.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151144/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-outside-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151144/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-outside-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151144/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-outside-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151144/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-outside-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151144/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-outside-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151144/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-outside-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151144/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-outside-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Hope’s earlier XC-focused Race EVO X2 2-piston brakeset has been out of productions for a while, leaving weight weenies still begging for the lightest the UK manufacturer had to offer. While the Races were light, it seems some riders felt they didn’t live up to the proven stopping power of other Hope brakes without adding heavier 4-piston calipers. In the meantime, Hope’s proven Tech 3 lever &amp; X2 calipers have been delivering excellent XC to trail stopping power at around 249g a set (also available in <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/11/25/hope-tech-3-duo-lever-pulls-2-hydraulic-brakes-with-1-hand-tech-3-x2-uno-does-too/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">great adaptive-use versions</a>!). But Hope knew they could do better.</p><h3>What’s new?</h3><p>The new XCR design makes a few key changes to reduce weight without sacrificing on performance. For Hope’s machined alloy fans, the new carbon brake lever is an obvious shift, rotating on new reduced friction lever pivot bushings. Carbon’s not really a big surprise with all of the other <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=hope+carbon\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">in-house Hope carbon</a> they’ve been getting up to in recent years.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside.jpg\" alt=\"Hope XCR lightweight MTB brakes, superlight &amp; powerful UK-made CNC-machined XC Trail mountain bike brakeset,&nbsp;carbon lever\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1000\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151137/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_carbon-brake-lever-inside-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The other big shift is the new minimalist master cylinder layout, now essentially integrated into the brake mount body that positions the lever pivot away from the bar. This configuration allows Hope to maintain their easy-to-bleed, large-volume hydraulic reservoir inside the boxy hollow structure, resulting in a stiff &amp; wide clamp to your bar.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151122/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_precision-machinning.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151122/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_precision-machinning.jpg\" alt=\"Hope XCR lightweight MTB brakes, superlight &amp; powerful UK-made CNC-machined XC Trail mountain bike brakeset,&nbsp;machingin detail\" width=\"2000\" height=\"750\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151122/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_precision-machinning.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151122/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_precision-machinning-297x111.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151122/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_precision-machinning-800x300.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151122/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlig