84.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151103/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_XCR-X2-set-1536x768.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151103/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_XCR-X2-set-696x348.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151103/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_XCR-X2-set-1068x534.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151103/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_XCR-X2-set-1920x960.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151103/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_XCR-X2-set-840x420.jpg 840w\"></a></p><p>Like everyone else in the industry fighting with component availability, Hope is working hard to meet increased demand. While their brakes are all made in-house, the new XCR is for the time being, manufactured on the CNC machines in the Hope R&amp;D lab. What that means is that although they are available right now, quantities are going to be limited for the foreseeable future. Act fast if you need to upgrade your stopping power and shed a few grams.</p><p>The new Hope XCR mountain bike brakes sell for £250 per brake (lever + caliper, front OR rear, rotors &amp; adapters available separately.) We haven’t heard yet explicitly, but the XCR brake lever should also be compatible with the flat mount version of the X2 caliper for those with a flat mount XC mountain bike frame.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-large-leaderboard-2\"></span></p><h3>First Trail Impressions</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151129/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_details-on-bike.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151129/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_details-on-bike.jpg\" alt=\"Hope XCR lightweight MTB brakes, superlight &amp; powerful UK-made CNC-machined XC Trail mountain bike brakeset,&nbsp;on bike\" width=\"2100\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151129/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_details-on-bike.jpg 2100w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151129/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_details-on-bike-297x170.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151129/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_details-on-bike-800x457.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151129/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_details-on-bike-120x69.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151129/Hope-XCR-lightweight-mountain-bike-brakes_superlight-powerful-CNC-XC-Trail-MTB-brakeset_made-in-UK_details-on-bike-768x439.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/31151129/Hope-XCR-lightweight-m